j\u00f8re for \u00e5 f\u00f8lge opp, sier Grethe Hartvigsen Larsen."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "0e4aade422cdf3466cca082d7bccac4007a77200b134b62ab9e274f65a3fc351"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-03-28T09:31:08.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Vandaler markerte skoleferiens start med \u00e5 knuse flere ruter p\u00e5 Vik\u00e5sen skole i Trondheim."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article9833730.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/IMG_31051.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/b8b42ad34836df7768bcb5151d5118143eb6f863.jpg?58da2d5c"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Ruteknusing p\u00e5 skole -adressa.no", "Glassk\u00e5r p\u00e5 gulvet", "Ingen mistenkte"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "b8b42ad34836df7768bcb5151d5118143eb6f863"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["h\u00e6rverk", "skole", "sluppet unna"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": "vik\u00e5sen"}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["s\u00f8r-tr\u00f8ndelag", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["wiktor pedersen", "\u00f8yvind eklo", "grethe hartvigsen larsen"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/trondheim"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article9833730.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/IMG_31051.jpg"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field": 